metadata.name: The Degen Show
metadata.description:
The year is 2025.  
     Elon has implanted chips into the brains of the masses so that we could see VR without a headset. 
     We have TV head Cats for pets, the Kongz are scaling skyscrapers, ACK is standing in every body of water on earth like a Degen Jesus, and hats have been replaced with Toadz. 
     The media has gained control and is streaming advertisement in our peripheral vision for a semi-subconscious mass manipulation, where the highest bidder is guaranteed the highest attention rate.  
     Privacy is no longer an option and resistance to the cancel-cultural flow is threatened with the reveal of your innermost thoughts and desires.  
     Better buy the dip. *KeK*
